Getting Started with Gauge
==========================

* Go to the demo site login page

Scenario Page Control
---------------------
* Check title login page
* Check Header on login page
* Check Status Message on login page
* Check Info Message on login page
* Check User name on login page
* Check password field on login page
* Check Login button

Scenario Login Success
----------------------
* Enter correct username on login page
* Enter correct password on login page
* Click login button on login page
* Check success login status message on login page

Scenario Login failed
----------------------
* Enter incorrect username on login page
* Enter incorrect password on login page
* Click login button on login page
* Check failed login status message on login page
